nexacro (19468)&gt; SD 00:09:31:318 file://C:/project_incubator/work_spaces/gstweb/WebContent/nxui/nexacro17lib/component/Grid/Grid.js(30159):Uncaught TypeError: Cannot read property ''_activate'' of null
